A php mysql db client wrapper implementations for common use.

Features
========
    - Vertical partitioning by table.
    - Horizontal sharding by table & shard_key.
        Directory-based partitioning.
    - A simple query builder.
        DML
            SELECT ... FROM ... WHERE ...
            INSERT ... INTO ... VALUES ...
            UPDATE ... SET ... WHERE ...
            DELETE FROM ... WHERE ...

Dependencies
============
    PHP: php 5.3.x
    Extensions:
        mysqli
        memcached
